Author: Alexey Seleznev [aut], Danzerzine [aut, cre], Netpeak [cph]
Maintainer: Danzerzine <dan@snop.agency>
Description: Modern, robust R interface to Yandex Metrica API with comprehensive
    support for Management API, Reporting API, Logs API, and Google Analytics
    compatible API. Features include advanced authentication, parallel processing,
    comprehensive error handling, and modern R programming practices while
    maintaining backward compatibility with existing scripts.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
